        '-min_cov_contig[k-mer coverage cutoff for contig-assembly of MetaPlatanus (default, 4 with MEGAHIT, 2 otherwise)]' \
        '-min_map_idt_binning[minimum identity (%) in read mapping for binning (default, 97)]' \
